text: Hemicladus dejeanii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Buquet in 1857. It is known from Brazil and French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Hemicladus dejeanii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1857
